end into the community.\r\nPurposeful and meaningful activities for residents and the community.\r\nExceptional care delivered consistently with love &amp; compassion.\r\nAbility &amp; desire to change and adapt to resident\'s needs.\r\nA gateway to the community where multi-generational interaction is supported.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">A PLACE WE CAN ALL CALL HOME</p>'),(2239,101,'_flexible_2_simple_contents_2_content','field_627142eda2b07'),(2240,102,'flexible','a:3:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:8:\"cta_itab\";i:2;s:14:\"simple_content\";}'),(2241,102,'_flexible','field_6259dde8e2c55'),(2242,102,'flexible_0_slide_0_title','This is title'),(2243,102,'_flexible_0_slide_0_title','field_6259de4685dd5'),(2244,102,'flexible_0_slide_0_image',''),(2245,102,'_flexible_0_slide_0_image','field_6259de3385dd4'),(2246,102,'flexible_0_slide_0_subtitle','This is subtitle'),(2247,102,'_flexible_0_slide_0_subtitle','field_6259de7585dd6'),(2248,102,'flexible_0_slide_0_buttons_0_button','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:5:\"CTA 1\";s:3:\"url\";s:1:\"#\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(2249,102,'_flexible_0_slide_0_buttons_0_button','field_6259de8f85dd8'),(2250,102,'flexible_0_slide_0_buttons','1'),(2251,102,'_flexible_0_slide_0_buttons','field_6259de7985dd7'),(2252,102,'flexible_0_slide','1'),(2253,102,'_flexible_0_slide','field_6259de2585dd3'),(2254,102,'flexible_0_active','1'),(2255,102,'_flexible_0_active','field_6259e17cbad76'),(2256,102,'flexible_0_slider_0_image',''),(2257,102,'_flexible_0_slider_0_image','field_6259de3385dd4'),(2258,102,'flexible_0_slider_0_title',''),(2259,102,'_flexible_0_slider_0_title','field_6259de4685dd5'),(2260,102,'flexible_0_slider_0_subtitle',''),(2261,102,'_flexible_0_slider_0_subtitle','field_6259de7585dd6'),(2262,102,'flexible_0_slider_0_button_1',''),(2263,102,'_flexible_0_slider_0_button_1','field_6259ebad93fb2'),(2264,102,'flexible_0_slider_0_button_2',''),(2265,102,'_flexible_0_slider_0_button_2','field_6259ebbd93fb3'),(2266,102,'flexible_0_slider'